      "text": "MAKKONEN, Pekka, SIAKAS, Kerstin and VAIDYA, Shakespeare, 2011. Teaching [[Knowledge Management]] by combining wikis and screen capture videos. UHOMOIBHI, James (ed.), Campus-Wide Information Systems. Online. 1 January 2011. Vol. 28, no. 5, p. 360–366. [Accessed 21 September 2023]. [https://doi.org/10.1108/10650741111181625 doi]."
